业平稳发展，预计部分省市展开试点也是由点到面逐步展开，再不断扩大覆盖面。」张波表示。 此前于 2018 年，住建部曾向广东、湖北、四川、江苏等六省发函，要求这些省份对商品房预售许可进行深入研究。近几年来，南京、杭州、苏州等城市曾在部分地块出让时尝试过现房销售，但杭州、南京在推行一段时间后，已暂停这一探索。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-24160237051bd401f720d5342777f7a8_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "202 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/582921835"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I74mUl874qJZAEAMaCDkxODE5NjMyIJeWkZ8GMBE4ygNABXIJNTgyOTIxODM1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1675989214.5668788", "card_id": "Q_582644358", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 67}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "三体舰队能以十分之一光速航行，是如何躲避前方障碍物的呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "三体舰队能以十分之一光速航行，是如何躲避前方障碍物的呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-c80393a00a3f7bc4f612cccd6bab197c_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "185 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/582644358"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I74mUl874qJZAEAMaCDkxNzU3ODkxIJrBiJ8GMAg4qAFABnIJNTgyNjQ0MzU4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1675989214.5675151", "card_id": "Q_458741991", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 17}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "大连蛇岛大约有两万条蛇，如果放两只蜜獾上去，大概多久能吃完？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "