足边前卫，假动作与过人如同南美球员一样，被称为英格兰盘带大师。巴恩斯踢左路，突破十分犀利，下底传中效率极高，86 年对阿根廷 70 多分钟替补登场后几乎靠着他一人的助攻扳平比分。 比尔兹利，驼背带球不抬头，但是技术极好，几乎不怎么丢球。 半决赛败给德国十分可惜，运气差了些而已。这只英格兰国家队，我认为是五十年内实力最强并最具观赏性的英格兰队。 期待未来英格兰国家队能够取得历史突破。拉什福德，芒特，贝林厄姆等人还是值得期待一下的。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-2a5c3dc95130a63f2a64291da2880594_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "47 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/582607347"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I74mUl874qJZAEAMaCDkxNzQ5NjMzINOwh58GMAM4OUArcgk1ODI2MDczNDd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "44_1675989214.5960877", "card_id": "Q_582787133", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 80}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么就算不买车也要考驾照呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "驾照必须要考嘛？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "47 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/582787133"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I74mUl874qJZAEAMaCDkxNzg5NzQ1IOeNjZ8GMAA4Y0Ascgk1ODI3ODcxMzN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "45_1675989214.5966241", "card_id": "Q_580346184", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 36}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价黄渤、梅婷主演的都市剧《打开生活的正确方式》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-bf4e84a0ba5185d95a4c13eb88a4a941_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "47 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/580346184"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I74mUl874qJZAEAMaCDkxMjQ3NjM3IJuEv54GMAA4MEAtcgk1ODAzNDYxODR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "